  <brief_title>Natural Supplements for Unipolar Depression</brief_title>
  <official_title>Phase 4 Study: An Open Study of the Efficacy and Tolerability in Unipolar Depression of Augmentation of the One-Carbon Cycle With L-Methionine, Betaine and Folate</official_title>
  <sponsors>
