  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study is being conducted to determine the clinical response rate for the regimen of
      L-methionine, betaine and folate for unipolar depression.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      The study is 6 weeks long, with 9 clinical visits.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
